ChangeList.Description: Updated the [Create](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-lifecycleworkflowscontainer-post-workflows?view=graph-rest-beta) operation for the [workflow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflow?view=graph-rest-beta) resource to now support the creation of up to 100 workflows, an increase from the previous limit of 50.

Updated the [Create](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-lifecycleworkflowscontainer-post-workflows?view=graph-rest-1.0) operation for the [workflow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflow?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource to now support the creation of up to 100 workflows, an increase from the previous limit of 50.
Added the **Update** operation to the [task](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-task?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **List** operation to [retrieve users that are in scope of execution conditions of a workflow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/workflow-list-executionscope?view=graph-rest-beta) in Lifecycle Workflows.

Added support for the **LifecycleWorkflows.ReadWrite.All** delegated and application permissions to the read and write operations of the [taskProcessingResult: resume](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-lifecycleworkflows-overview?view=graph-rest-beta) API call.

Added the **insights** relationship to the [lifecycleWorkflowsContainer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-lifecycleWorkflowsContainer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [insights](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-insights?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods. Insights provide aggregate data about the health and processing of lifecycle workflows in a tenant. They include the number of total, successful, and failed workflow executions, tasks processed, and users processed across all workflows for the tenant for a given period.

Added the [topTasksProcessedSummary](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-insights-toptasksprocessedsummary?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [insights](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-insights?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [topWorkflowsProcessedSummary](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-insights-topworkflowsprocessedsummary?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [insights](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-insights?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [workflowsProcessedByCategory](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-insights-workflowsprocessedbycategory?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [insights](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-insights?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [workflowsProcessedSummary](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-insights-workflowsprocessedsummary?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [insights](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-insights?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the **lifecycleWorkflows** relationship to the [identityGovernance](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [lifecycleWorkflowsContainer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-lifecycleWorkflowsContainer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. This resource is the entry point for Azure AD Lifecycle Workflows capabilities that are available through Microsoft Graph.
Added the [workflowTemplate](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflowTemplate?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods.

Added the [workflow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflow?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods. Represents a lifecycle workflow object.
Added the [task](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-task?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods. Represents the tasks in a lifecycle workflow.

Added the [taskDefinition](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-taskDefinition?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods. Represents the pre-defined tasks for different categories of lifecycle workflows.

Added the [customTaskExtension](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-customTaskExtension?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods. Represents extensibility capabilities that allows you to integrate lifecycle workflows with Azure Logic Apps.

Added the [lifecycleManagementSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-lifecycleManagementSettings?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods. Represents the tenant-wide settings for Azure AD Lifecycle Workflows.

Added the [deletedItemContainer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/deletedItemContainer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods. Use this container to manage deleted lifecycle workflows.
Added the [workflowVersion](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflowVersion?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods.
Added the [run](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-run?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods.
Added the [taskProcessingResult](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-taskProcessingResult?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods.
Added the [taskReport](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-taskReport?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods.
Added the [userProcessingResult](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-userProcessingResult?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and its associated methods.

Added support for the `LifecycleWorkflows.Read.All` delegated and application permissions to the read operations of [Azure AD lifecycle workflows](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-lifecycleworkflows-overview?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added support for the `LifecycleWorkflows.ReadWrite.All` delegated and application permissions to the read and write operations of [Azure AD lifecycle workflows](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-lifecycleworkflows-overview?view=graph-rest-beta).
Added the `mover` member to the **lifecycleWorkflowCategory** enum type.
Added the `mover` member to the **lifecycleTaskCategory** enum type.
Added the `mover` member to the **lifecycleWorkflowCategory** enum type.
Added the `mover` member to the **lifecycleTaskCategory** enum type.

Added the **insights** relationship to the [lifecycleWorkflowsContainer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-lifecycleWorkflowsContainer?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [topTasksProcessedSummary](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identityGovernance-insights-topTasksProcessedSummary?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [insights](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-insights?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [topWorkflowsProcessedSummary](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identityGovernance-insights-topWorkflowsProcessedSummary?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [insights](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-insights?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [workflowsProcessedByCategory](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identityGovernance-insights-workflowsProcessedByCategory?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [insights](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-insights?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [workflowsProcessedSummary](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identityGovernance-insights-workflowsProcessedSummary?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [insights](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-insights?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [activate](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-workflow-activate?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [workflow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflow?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [createNewVersion](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-workflow-createnewversion?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [workflow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflow?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [restore](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-workflow-restore?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [workflow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflow?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [resume](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-taskprocessingresult-resume?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [taskProcessingResult](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-taskProcessingResult?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [summary](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-run-summary?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [run](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-run?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [summary](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-taskreport-summary?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [taskReport](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-taskReport?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the [summary](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/identitygovernance-userprocessingresult-summary?view=graph-rest-1.0) method to the [userProcessingResult](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-userProcessingResult?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.

Added the **emailSettings** property to the [lifecycleManagementSettings](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identityGovernance-lifecycleManagementSettings?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **authorizedApps** property to the [customTaskExtensionCallbackConfiguration](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-customtaskextensioncallbackconfiguration?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the **isEnabled** property to the [workflowBase](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflowBase?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. **workflowBase** is an entity type that's inherited by the following derived types in Lifecycle Workflows: [workflow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflow?view=graph-rest-beta) and [workflowVersion](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflowVersion?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added the **isSchedulingEnabled** property to the [workflowBase](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflowBase?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.  **workflowBase** is an entity type that's inherited by the following derived types in Lifecycle Workflows: [workflow](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflow?view=graph-rest-beta) and [workflowVersion](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/identitygovernance-workflowVersion?view=graph-rest-beta).

Added the **maximumRetries** property to the [customExtensionClientConfiguration](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/customExtensionClientConfiguration?view=graph-rest-1.0) resource.
